Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.11,0:01:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了  悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.15,0:01:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点点的把力量传给我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.32,0:01:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.45,0:01:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翅膀已经能很轻松地成型了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.14,0:02:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜  时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.15,0:02:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  那今天到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.74,0:02:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,12点  零时迷子么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量回复了好是好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:02:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这感觉总
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微有点  肚子饿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去下面吃点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电视剧重播
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.48,0:03:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电视剧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指编出来的故事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.44,0:03:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要关掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理惠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.61,0:03:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么那家伙被打了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.43,0:03:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是  一般突然要被Kiss了总会不愿意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.04,0:03:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是Kiss这种程度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,程  程度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  大家都在看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.73,0:04:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好怕啊  泰莉亚露
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧的  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为你们这样的行动和华丽的衣服才引人注目的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  花朵要绽放难道还需要犹豫吗  希德内
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}摇篮庭院（cradle  garden）：爱染他·泰莉亚露的自在法\N可以将在这个世界存在的红世之徒的异样感完全隐藏\N战斗时和封绝拥有相同机能  对普通的火雾战士来说犹如蚁地狱般的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不希望\N听你这个被我的摇篮庭院所保护的家伙说这种臭屁的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  喂  泰莉亚露  可以吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.85,0:05:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但  能否请再稍等会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么自在式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎快发现哥哥寻找的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得才找到  被谁抢走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可就不好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为  为了不给别人拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要关起来对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用我们的摇篮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请吃了那个以外的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.04,0:05:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  知不知道八音盒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}八音盒：爱染他所持有的宝具  不管如何复杂的自在法  一旦装进便能无限使用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八音盒  是指音乐盒么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:06:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  虽然一般都是这么叫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但称为八音盒的话作为音乐来说不是更优雅些么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:10.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是和这个自在法一起使用的宝具吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣响的旋律非常好听哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现  现在还玩躲避球什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  一点事也没
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还好中止了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果再那样继续的话可糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个可算重伤了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.47,0:07:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  坂井
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于平井同学的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  虽然你们经常一起来上学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  没没  什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然说只不过是接吻嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:08:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是没那么简单的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这个我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是随便的话  稍后就会滑溜溜的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.87,0:08:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这个意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢  总觉得Kiss也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊  你是说这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  说的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kiss  昨天悠二的感觉也很怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教我的并没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  原来在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在查什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:08:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么  也不是什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心也没问题的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:10.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,池同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.18,0:09:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才也说了吧  只是和平井同学关系好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没恋爱的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐  我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的状态如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头会嗡嗡响的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟  荣太  脸上的伤是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这个是给球打了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启作  荣太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉酒也腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你搞什么  你搞什么是在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kiss到底有什么意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  但为什么问这种问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:09:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看似简单却很难回答的问题呢  小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你说去查过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算去图书馆查书  也只查到以前知道的那些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样的做法是知道  也看过别人做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感到别人认为的意思和我所知道的意思好像完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想千草的话一定知道这个的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小说或文学之类的读过没
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为亚拉斯托尔说过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加入个人主观的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.74,0:10:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对恰当的分析理性的思索毫无作用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.31,0:10:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚拉斯托尔先生好像是在远方代替父亲的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有很了不起的见解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.01,0:10:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是呢  小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.15,0:11:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是呢  小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.61,0:11:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候  这样说反而不能理解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.47,0:11:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,资料上所记载的只有现存的事实而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.14,0:11:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但小夏娜所考虑的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.35,0:11:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却是这以外的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.77,0:11:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说模模糊糊没有完整的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  是关于心和感情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心和感情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该知道身体的相互接触是深爱之情的表现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.70,0:11:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  Kiss也是其中一种吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,握手和拥抱之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是这样没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好  比如和亚拉斯托尔先生这么做的话没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那和小悠能做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:12:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新想一下的话  也挺不好意思的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.23,0:12:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是所说内容的中心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.77,0:12:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且说是Kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲脸颊和嘴对嘴的意思可完全不一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.99,0:12:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和  和悠二嘴对嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不要这样  不想被亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千草
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.15,0:12:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能被亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就算是亚拉斯托尔先生也不能做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.51,0:12:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.83,0:12:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我呢  是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴对嘴的Kiss  是像发誓一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.52,0:12:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  用自己的全部来发誓也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把自己的全部托付出去也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种发誓的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是Kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点累了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托零时迷子的福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的力量每到零点就会恢复吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  就是指不会变老吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己去确认如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.90,0:13:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然可能会花很长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.94,0:13:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.19,0:13:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会和夏娜永远在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.71,0:13:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事要拜托你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.39,0:14:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千草  借下电话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.23,0:14:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但小夏娜  到去学校的时间了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.82,0:14:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.28,0:14:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千草
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换人接了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.85,0:14:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次通话  夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下的名字是亚拉斯托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  原来是亚拉斯托尔先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.09,0:14:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平井缘总是承蒙您照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.26,0:14:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是坂井悠二的母亲  名叫千草
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.22,0:14:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是  给您添了不少麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那特地来联系究竟有何贵干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.82,0:14:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是平井缘的事  请直说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  啊  还有那个请称之为夏娜就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是这么叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  亚拉斯托尔先生也公认了的昵称呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.94,0:15:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.36,0:15:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  我想说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实  是昨天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.03,0:15:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠  小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是否定夫人的恋爱观
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像昨天的那些话请不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.06,0:15:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜说出去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是我硬逼着她说出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:16:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论何时  能听到那个小夏娜说这些的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是被深深信赖着的证据呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来小夏娜是被很重视地抚养长大的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.62,0:16:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是非常单纯的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会诱发夏娜像昨天一样和坂井悠二欠考虑的接触的发言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请尽量小心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的意思我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人非常明白事理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来就能全交给您了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.75,0:16:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.75,0:16:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.36,0:16:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以再和您谈谈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜和说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个高贵而又厉害的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我以为在另一方面却有着非常幼小而脆弱的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:58.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请继续
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  那失礼的说一句
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感到小夏娜对人的感情和心都很陌生  有着毫无防备之处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.12,0:17:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我家的悠二是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,困扰年轻人的东西出现时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那纯真无垢的孩子会多么抵触呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.38,0:17:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天我感觉到了这危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才说了那些话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是  还太早了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想花上数年时间  让她经历各种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.31,0:17:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后慢慢地告诉她会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦不会由我们随心所欲地发生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.51,0:17:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  我想教她应该教的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不会有太早这说法的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也为了小夏娜自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且女孩子可是比外观看起来早熟很多的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前所做的不适当的发言可以撤回么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了大言不惭的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜的话没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.79,0:18:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要好好教她的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.75,0:18:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就应该会从内心找到属于自己的做法和正确答案的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种信赖应该有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.09,0:18:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近了  好近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像在找什么东西似的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  不愧是索拉特的「欲望的嗅觉」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种令人厌烦的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是火雾战士了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火雾战士  好想要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多要给察觉到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该明白火雾战士的出现只是时间问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  打算如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.33,0:19:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再设些机关  以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.75,0:19:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始吧  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一步  先去打个招呼如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为要找出来  是很简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  刚才亚拉斯托尔在电话里说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天的事怎么怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.84,0:19:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.49,0:19:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你绝对绝对不做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话  做了坂井同学的份
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一直都吃饭团
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.09,0:20:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.01,0:20:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.31,0:20:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.79,0:20:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从哪个开始吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真伤脑筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀  买了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岂止「不少」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.73,0:20:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,购物才刚开始啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.59,0:20:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是在青黄不接时又来了大客户
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美丽的杀戮者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种地方干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.72,0:21:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠不住的色男
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  给你介绍一下  泰莉亚露
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.96,0:21:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在火雾战士里也屈指可数的杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.33,0:21:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悼词朗诵者——玛裘莉·顿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那是蹂躏的爪牙的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.99,0:21:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.03,0:21:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  这些人没拿着我想要的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为很简单就能找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.36,0:21:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却不是猎物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  所以走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.87,0:21:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥既然说了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.30,0:21:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙不是红世之徒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.37,0:21:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放过他们没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.58,0:22:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是放过他们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是被放过了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.76,0:22:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴  笨蛋马尔克
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.67,0:22:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那以后和老妈说了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.86,0:22:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没必要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.59,0:22:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.25,0:22:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个  加紧锻炼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.26,0:22:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让母亲蒙羞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.89,0:22:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠  小夏娜  饭准备好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.81,0:22:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.61,0:22:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.45,0:22:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不和你做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.76,0:22:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.79,0:22:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贽殿遮那
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.14,0:24:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,思念悠二的少女尽全力的战斗宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.00,0:24:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受挑战的夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.15,0:24:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那时「爱染他」——泰莉亚露的陷阱正袭来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.36,0:24:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回  在摇篮里盛开的花
